      <title>拉里奥哈债权人在纽约因债券纠纷获赔 4000 万美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/la-rioja-creditors-win-40-million-in-ny-court-over-junk-bonds</link>
